	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I might be able to explain the missing mic. Over time some of the analog parts of it would break...causing a buzzing in the audio line coming from the mic circuit...a quick fix is to take out the mic so you don't get the annoying mic noise mixed in.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


